> 20 May - Ataturk’s last national tour (to Mersin) He stressed on Hatay republic problem
> 5 July - Turkish army in Hatay (by treaty)
> 2 September - Hatay Republic was founded, Tayfur Sokmen was elected as the Hatay president
> 28 October - Ankara Radio began broadcasting
> 10 November - Ataturk died
> 11 November - İsmet İnönü was elected as the new president
New government